00:18:09.690 --> 00:18:13.940
dan merusak kebun jeruk Bellemere-san.

00:18:13.940 --> 00:18:14.630
Hah?

00:18:17.810 --> 00:18:19.020
Kolonel!

00:18:23.740 --> 00:18:26.410
Terima kasih, Nami!
Aku merasa puas!

00:18:26.410 --> 00:18:28.850
